open new terminal - mod+Enter
open dmenu - mod+D
kill active window - mod+Shift+Q
split a window vertically - mod+V
split a window horizontally - mod+H
change focus - mod+Left/Right/Up/Down
move window - mod+Shift+Left/Right/Up/Down
switch to another workspace - mod+0-9
move focused container - mod+Shift+0-9
toggle floating - mod+Shift+Space
tabbed mode - mod+W
stacking mode - mod+S
default mode - mod+E
reload the configuration file - mod+C
restart i3wm - mod+Shift+R
exit i3wm - mod+Shift+E

pwd - path of the folder
cd - change directory
ls - view contents of a folder
cat - used to list the contents of a file
cp - copy files
mv - move files
mkdir - make a new folder
rmdir - delete a folder
rm - delete files
touch - create a new file
locate/find - find file
df - report of disk space usage
jobs - display all current tasks
kill - manual deactivation of the program
ping - check connectivity status
uname - Unix Name
top - display a list of running processes
history - running history command
zip/unzip - compress and decompress files

Polybar:

УСТАНОВКА:
Arch:
 mkdir ~/build
 cd ~/build
 git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/polybar.git
 cd ~/build/polybar
 makepkg -sri

КОНФИГ:
 В /home/username/.config/polybar положить конфиг из /usr/share/doc/polybar.

rus config:
polybar-config-rus.txt

polybar themes:
https://github.com/adi1090x/polybar-themes
